tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE sales (
    sale_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    customer_id INT,
    sale_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (vehicle_id) REFERENCES vehicles(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES customers(customer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE reviews (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    customer_id INT,
    rating INT,
    review_text TEXT
);
